Title: MoneyBox for WinForms
Description:
MoneyBox is a GUI Control use to format a number input to money format. 
It is like a textbox, but only allows numbers.
It' is for WinForms .Net Developers.
You'll no longer have to controls the input data, neither confuse de user.
It's developed in C#.NET Framework 3.5
